---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="Resume" description="조성덕 이력서">

  <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
    <p style="font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin: 0 0 0.25rem;">4년 경력의 ML Engineer</p>
  </div>

  <div style="border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 1.75rem;">
    <h2 style="font-size: 0.6875rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-tertiary); margin: 0 0 1.25rem;">Experience</h2>
    <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.875rem;">

      <div>
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; gap: 1rem; align-items: baseline;">
          <span style="font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-primary);">뷰노</span>
          <span style="font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--text-tertiary); white-space: nowrap;">2022.3 – 현재</span>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin: 0.125rem 0 0.25rem;">ML Engineer</p>
        <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-tertiary); margin: 0;">흉부 X-ray · 폐 CT · 디지털 병리 진단 AI 제품 연구개발</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; gap: 1rem; align-items: baseline;">
          <span style="font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-primary);">고려대 고성능비주얼컴퓨팅 연구실</span>
          <span style="font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--text-tertiary); white-space: nowrap;">2019.6 – 2022.2</span>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin: 0.125rem 0 0.25rem;">Research Assistant</p>
        <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-tertiary); margin: 0;">딥러닝 기반 의료 영상 처리 연구 및 국제 챌린지 주최</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 1.75rem;">
    <h2 style="font-size: 0.6875rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-tertiary); margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">Conferences</h2>
    <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.375rem;">

      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; gap: 1rem; align-items: baseline;">
        <span style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-primary);">ECR</span>
        <span style="font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--text-tertiary); white-space: nowrap;">2026</span>
      </div>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; gap: 1rem; align-items: baseline;">
        <span style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-primary);">KCR</span>
        <span style="font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--text-tertiary); white-space: nowrap;">2025</span>
      </div>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; gap: 1rem; align-items: baseline;">
        <span style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-primary);">KCR</span>
        <span style="font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--text-tertiary); white-space: nowrap;">2024</span>
      </div>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; gap: 1rem; align-items: baseline;">
        <span style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-primary);">RSNA</span>
        <span style="font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--text-tertiary); white-space: nowrap;">2023</span>
      </div>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; gap: 1rem; align-items: baseline;">
        <span style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-primary);">KCR</span>
        <span style="font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--text-tertiary); white-space: nowrap;">2023</span>
      </div>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; gap: 1rem; align-items: baseline;">
        <span style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-primary);">KSSR</span>
        <span style="font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--text-tertiary); white-space: nowrap;">2022</span>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top: 1.75rem;">
    <h2 style="font-size: 0.6875rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-tertiary); margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">Education</h2>
    <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem;">

      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; gap: 1rem; align-items: baseline;">
        <span style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-primary);">컴퓨터과학 석사 · 고려대학교</span>
        <span style="font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--text-tertiary); white-space: nowrap;">2020 – 2022</span>
      </div>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; gap: 1rem; align-items: baseline;">
        <span style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-primary);">컴퓨터공학 학사 · 울산과학기술원 (UNIST)</span>
        <span style="font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--text-tertiary); white-space: nowrap;">2015 – 2020</span>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

</PageLayout>
